{
  "title": "midnight-craving jamaican yautia bake",
  "description": "a bitter, creamy, midnight-craving jamaican dish featuring yautia, perfect for when you can't sleep and need a sweet fix. the tandoor adds a nice smoky flavor, while keeping it sugar-free-friendly.",
